              class="text-accent-light">--template</code
            > shows unresolved tokens. <code class="text-accent-light">gtl env</code> defaults to <code
              class="text-accent-light">show</code
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6 sm:py-5 border-b border-surface-border last:border-b-0">
          <span class="font-mono text-white text-base font-semibold">env sync</span>
          <p class="text-base text-muted mt-2">
            Re-read env from <code class="text-accent-light">.treeline.yml</code>, update env file, refresh editor.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6 sm:py-5 border-b border-surface-border last:border-b-0">
          <span class="font-mono text-white text-base font-semibold">db name</span>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
            <span
              class="font-mono text-xs text-yellow-400/80 border border-yellow-400/20 bg-yellow-400/5 px-2 py-0.5 rounded"
